{"tid":1860211,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢個時刻我地一定要團結，罷工先有威力同希望","createTime":"2020-02-03T14:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T15:32:41.000Z","uid":34816,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66ae14feffd623af52a2ada3203f22ccd4a68400","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"我知好多人呢一刻係期望緊有先驅者，能夠透過罷工等工業行動去迫使政權跪低，之後再根據經驗同情況去組織以後既行動。<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知，醫護罷工係咁耐以黎第一次真正有威攝力既工業行動，我地唔可以要佢地孤獨行動，如果呢一次行動輸左，會極大咁打擊接落黎以後唔同既工業行動，我地一定要齊上齊落，用實際行動去支援佢地！<br />\n<br />\n我係到承諾，如果罷工既醫護事後有任何事要面對，需要支援，我願意盡一切能力捐款去支援佢地，捐身家都會捐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地願意嗎？"},{"pid":"ed6d8b8f8b9ac88603a08ab2cf0d553a072a26d3","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c9816106102bb42b2f465656eff82549c555c5","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e32b74be2b3e7fa32e2f5cd6b72c61b5ee3b7e5","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"佢地做得先驅，我地一定要做後援<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359eb3c2a911d00e17384f7f9efb530e5d674f5d","tid":1860211,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:06:18.000Z","msg":"我願意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a78658a734cd73bffffb6fce5851060eef5c6cd","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4894ec2b41f9cd6fdb6c01228b8206989eebaf","tid":1860211,"uid":102491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"支持你地<br />\n光復香港 跪啦臭閪柒婆<br />\n#手動轉<br />\n<br />\n香港實在太荒誕。<br />\n<br />\nTrain一個警察，只需要幾個月。<br />\n而考警察只需5科合格，體能又合格就得，<br />\n無太多學歷要求，所以毅進畢業就得。<br />\n<br />\nTrain一位護士，起碼要4年時間，<br />\n要出placement，又要讀好多理論，<br />\nTrain一位化驗師/放射治療/物理治療等醫護專業，<br />\n都要4年以上，又係要好長實習期，理論亦唔容易。<br />\n考入去讀呢啲醫護專業，點止要5科合格呢？<br />\n你DSE冇返幾個5，A-level冇返幾個C都入唔到。<br />\n毅進仔⋯以前HKCEE已經畀人踢走，點升AL？<br />\n<br />\nTrain一位醫生呢？普通科咪5-6年，專科起碼10年。<br />\n讀得醫嘅個個都係尖子，精英中的精英。<br />\n<br />\n結果呢？一句「止暴制亂」，警察坐享無限行政資源，<br />\nOT無限補水，個個都Full gear上陣，<br />\n過多兩個月又有新玩具玩。<br />\n醫護即使緊守崗位，任勞任怨，OT冇補足，<br />\n公立醫院日日都過full capacity，但竟然要cut資源。<br />\n一個口罩，一件PPE，都要珍而重之。<br />\n因為唔止醫護同工要著，病人都要著。<br />\n醫護就算冇N95，冇ASTM-Level 2口罩都要頂硬上。<br />\n<br />\n半年社運，無一警員殉職，連重傷都唔覺得有。<br />\n但一場即將來臨的瘟疫，<br />\n可以一夜奪去數十，甚至數百前線醫護性命。<br />\n<br />\n散仔會會長可以喪鬧比自己高級的官員都冇後果，<br />\n班醫護隨時因工送命，喊罷工，<br />\n即刻畀人道德強姦，要人地緊守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n即使警隊集體辭職，只要大規模招人，<br />\n幾個月又有人賣命。<br />\n但係若果一名資深醫護殉職，<br />\n要幾耐先有同樣人才可以取代？<br />\n即使只係一個普通醫護，<br />\n都要幾年時間先train返個出黎。<br />\n<br />\n試問生活響一個咁畸型嘅社會，邊個會唔反抗？<br />\n<br />\n#政府高官又點會諗呢D<br />\n#政府最緊要維穩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tw6EOJm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTw6EOJm.png&h=e2ebc40b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fe274bebec3531a24b387c8a0f4767fb861e7c2","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8997c8022c423e31c63361b445862c87a0b35d6","tid":1860211,"uid":164863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"我願意<br />\n一齊罷"},{"pid":"fbc31be723de15dda1950ac525d7169b64fd2855","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"669f2d103f87e45b40381f356f4430a6ae5f8661","tid":1860211,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c37b743aea2b194335c63332b47c52422b02b95","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368f7eff246b33915f02f564a379bccd681a5c08","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e548fbcaa837ca74eb3f923205fb078a82af0b7e","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67ffc912beead6fc1fd0c7d8d36a76a15baf21e","tid":1860211,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"eafe792ea7675d3ce0880a120f6b4f8680698614","tid":1860211,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"醫護